<emphasis id="218AF01ABE78FFA0FCB5DB63FCBCF8AA" bold="true" box="[810,830,1798,1822]" pageId="2" pageNumber="29">1.</emphasis>
Male head (frontal). 
<emphasis id="218AF01ABE78FFA0FBBDDB63FBB7F8AA" bold="true" box="[1058,1077,1798,1822]" pageId="2" pageNumber="29">2.</emphasis>
Female head (frontal). 
<emphasis id="218AF01ABE78FFA0FE97DB4CFE99F8F5" bold="true" box="[264,283,1833,1857]" pageId="2" pageNumber="29">3.</emphasis>
Male antennal flagellomeres 9­12. 
<emphasis id="218AF01ABE78FFA0FD5CDB4CFD54F8F5" bold="true" box="[707,726,1833,1857]" pageId="2" pageNumber="29">4.</emphasis>
Male antennal flagellomere 5. 
